      • isCanary

        public boolean isCanary
        Whether or not the generator is a 'canary' generator. Like the canary in a coal mine, canary generators indicate a problem with the grid. Canary generators provide a means to ensure a load profile can be met, since AMES does not yet handle reserves/reserve markets.
